| 8     | `^`                          | Bitwise XOR                   |            |            |
| 9     | `                            | `                             | Bitwise OR |            |
| 10    | `&&`                         | Logical AND                   |            |            |
| 11    | `                            |                               | `          | Logical OR |
| 12    | `=` `+=` `-=` `*=` `/=` `%=` | Assignment Operators          |            |            |
